\f0\b\fs26 \cf0 Region two - Angry Owlbear
\b0 .
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs26 An ancient and bitter Owlbear lives here. It carries an old wound that slows it down somewhat, but it\'92s power and size makes up for its disability. It's been in the dungeon so long that it's become touched by the Obelisk of Insanity and has gained a strange psychic power. It occasionally leaves the dungeon to hunt, but otherwise exists on a diet of giant rats and stray wanderers. It is a powerful monster and it\'92s lair is littered with treasure. In no way should the GM hide the fact that the Owlbear is very tough, but that the party could flee if they need to.
\f1\fs24 \
